   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Churn Reason Miner\\n\",\"**NLP Project 86 of 100** — Extract likely churn reasons from customer feedback using text clustering and keyword analysis.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Cluster negative feedback to find churn themes.\\n\",\"2. Use TF-IDF + K-Means for unsupervised theme discovery.\\n\",\"3. Quantify churn reasons for business action.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns\\nfrom sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\\nfrom sklearn.cluster import KMeans\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nsns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nSEED = 42; rng = np.random.default_rng(SEED)\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Synthetic churn feedback\\nreasons = {\\n    'Price': ['Too expensive','Prices keep going up','Found a cheaper alternative','Not worth the price','Subscription cost too high'] * 15,\\n    'Support': ['Support was unhelpful','Long wait times for help','Could never reach anyone','Terrible customer service','Support tickets ignored'] * 12,\\n    'Features': ['Missing features I need','Product is too basic','Competitors have better features','No API integration','Lacks customization'] * 10,\\n    'Quality': ['Too many bugs','App keeps crashing','Performance is slow','Data loss issues','Unreliable service'] * 13,\\n}\\n\\nrows = []\\nfor reason, texts in reasons.items():\\n    for t in texts:\\n        rows.append({'feedback': t + ' ' + rng.choice(['unfortunately','sadly','disappointed','frustrated','leaving']), 'true_reason': reason})\\n\\ndf = pd.DataFrame(rows).sample(frac=1, random_state=SEED).reset_index(drop=True)\\nprint(f'Shape: {df.shape}'); print(df['true_reason'].value_counts())\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Theme Discovery via Clustering\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"tfidf = TfidfVectorizer(max_features=3000, stop_words='english')\\nX = tfidf.fit_transform(df['feedback'])\\n\\nkm = KMeans(n_clusters=4, random_state=SEED, n_init=10)\\ndf['cluster'] = km.fit_predict(X)\\n\\nterms = tfidf.get_feature_names_out()\\nfor i in range(4):\\n    top = [terms[j] for j in km.cluster_centers_[i].argsort()[-5:][::-1]]\\n    print(f'Cluster {i}: {top}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Cluster vs true reason cross-tab\\nct = pd.crosstab(df['cluster'], df['true_reason'])\\nprint(ct)\\n\\nfig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8,5))\\nct.plot(kind='bar', stacked=True, ax=ax)\\nax.set_title('Cluster vs True Churn Reason'); ax.set_xlabel('Cluster')\\nplt.tight_layout(); plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Churn reason distribution\\nfig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8,4))\\ndf['true_reason'].value_counts().plot(kind='bar', ax=ax, color='coral', edgecolor='black')\\nax.set_title('Churn Reasons Distribution'); ax.set_ylabel('Count')\\nplt.tight_layout(); plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Text clustering effectively identifies churn themes** from unstructured feedback.\\n\",\"- **Price and quality are the top churn drivers** in this dataset.\\n\",\"- **Actionable insights**: address pricing concerns and improve product stability.\\n\",\"- **For production, automate this pipeline** to continuously monitor churn signals.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
